#. module: shoe_maker
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:shoe_maker.welcome_article_body
msgid "<strong>How to use this Odoo Industry Package</strong>"
msgstr "<strong>Sådan bruges denne Odoo-branchepakke</strong>"

#. module: shoe_maker
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:shoe_maker.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Scenario 1: </strong>The simplest way to add products to an order is "
"to directly select your services from the <strong>Product Catalog</strong>. "
"Just click the \"Product Catalog\" button in your sales order lines and "
"select\n"
"        the products you wish to sell. Note that you can filter products "
"services by leveraging the filters in the sidebar on the left side of the "
"screen!"
msgstr ""
"<strong>Scenarie 1: </strong> Den nemmeste måde at tilføje produkter til en "
"ordre på er at vælge dine tjenester direkte fra <strong>produktkataloget</"
"strong>. Klik blot på knappen \"Produktkatalog\" i dine salgsordrelinjer, og "
"vælg\n"
"        de produkter, du ønsker at sælge. Bemærk, at du kan filtrere "
"produkter og tjenester ved hjælp af filtrene i sidepanelet til venstre på "
"skærmen!"

#. module: shoe_maker
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:shoe_maker.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Scenario 1:</strong> Most products need a human assessment as the "
"remaining quantity cannot be automatically computed. For those, a Recurring "
"Task is created in the Project App. This task reappears every week, and you "
"can\n"
"            personalize it with a checklist to avoid forgetting anything."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Scenarie 1:</strong> De fleste produkter skal vurderes manuelt, da "
"den resterende mængde ikke kan beregnes automatisk. For disse produkter "
"oprettes der en tilbagevendende opgave i Projekterappen. Opgaven vises hver "
"uge, og du kan\n"
"            tilpasse den med en tjekliste, så du ikke glemmer noget."

#. module: shoe_maker
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:shoe_maker.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Scenario 2:</strong> For products that can be tracked, such as laces "
"and soles, you can use automated purchases. To try it, confirm a new <font "
"class=\"text-o-color-5\">order adding i</font>\n"
"            <strong>\n"
"                <font class=\"text-o-color-5\">\n"
"                    <span style=\"font-weight: normal;\">nsoles with size "
"40-42</span>\n"
"                </font>\n"
"            </strong>\n"
"            <font class=\"text-o-color-5\">.</font>"
msgstr ""
"<strong>Scenarie 2:</strong> For produkter, der kan spores, såsom snørebånd "
"og såler, kan du bruge automatiserede indkøb. For at prøve det skal du "
"bekræfte en ny <font class=\"text-o-color-5\">ordre ved at tilføje</font>\n"
"            <strong>\n"
"               <font class=\"text-o-color-5\">\n"
"                    <span style=\"font-weight: normal;\"> indlægssåler i "
"størrelse 40-42</span>\n"
"                </font>\n"
"           </strong>\n"
"            <font class=\"text-o-color-5\">.</font>"

#. module: shoe_maker
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:shoe_maker.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Scenario 2:</strong> Oftentimes, services are bundled together. You "
"can toggle the \"Quotation Templates\" setting in your <strong>Settings app "
"</strong>in order to create, edit and load quotation templates in your\n"
"        sales order."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Scenarie 2:</strong> Tjenester tilbydes ofte som pakkeløsninger. Du "
"kan aktivere indstillingen \"Tilbudsskabeloner\" i din <strong>Indstillinge-"
"app</strong> for at oprette, redigere og indlæse tilbudsskabeloner i dine\n"
"        salgsordrer."

#. module: shoe_maker
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:shoe_maker.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"All installed Apps are available on your Odoo homescreen. The main Apps "
"you'll be using in your day-to-day are :"
msgstr ""
"Alle installerede apps er tilgængelige på din Odoo-startskærm. De vigtigste "
"apps, du vil bruge dagligt, er:"

#. module: shoe_maker
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:shoe_maker.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"At the end of your service, remember to close your register. To do so, in "
"the Point of Sale App, select \"Close Register\" in the top-right menu."
msgstr ""
"Husk at afslutte kasse, når du er færdig med at betjene kunden. Vælg \"Luk "
"kasse\" i menuen øverst til højre i POS-appen."

#. module: shoe_maker
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:shoe_maker.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Billing efficiently your customers for their orders is paramount for your "
"business and to help you make this as easy as possible, this Odoo package "
"comes with the <strong>Point of Sale App</strong>."
msgstr ""
"En effektiv afregning af dine kunders ordrer er afgørende for din "
"virksomhed. For at hjælpe dig med dette tilbyder Odoo <strong>POS-appen</"
"strong>."

